{"tid":378212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門兩名廢老涉網上發怖假消息被捕","createTime":"2017-08-28T10:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-29T12:19:37.000Z","uid":10780,"like":101,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0e579e30b4fe757776508c4c62479eb80a40de","tid":378212,"uid":10780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:13:55.000Z","msg":"澳門司警扣留2名73歲和68歲的兄妹，他們涉嫌在網上發佈不實消息，包括聲稱政府封鎖在筷子基停車場發現5具遺體的消息。司警表示，有人未證實消息真確，就用手機通訊軟件「微信」（WeChat），轉載該不實消息到至少6個聊天群組、30個私人對話中。司警會以觸犯侵犯行使公共當局權力之法人罪，移送他們到檢察院。司警又表示，案件仍在調查，不排除有更多人涉案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：蘋果日報<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"178aa00431dcaa7e0290e7b3d88cceb936669c37","tid":378212,"uid":10780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170828&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57139771\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170828%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57139771&d=qDUpWIL4Tt1KJD2AWblf6PiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=a0719162\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170828%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D57139771&h=89c8337e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170828&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=57139771</a><br />\n【天鴿襲澳】2老翁被捕！涉WeChat謠傳政府暪停車場5死"},{"pid":"c8e21e936beb3bb843f15488f6ac1b15291cf84c","tid":378212,"uid":192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T10:17:41.000Z","msg":"原告變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f20b9389ea1359ad9862fe520f77cb386f0d9f7","tid":378212,"uid":9328,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7